### 1. Initiate product
POST http://localhost:8080/agilepm/v1/tenants/tenant-a/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "product-001",
  "name": "AgilePM Platform",
  "description": "Product used to manage Scrum planning",
  "productOwnerId": "owner-001"
}

### 2. Schedule release
POST http://localhost:8080/agilepm/v1/tenants/tenant-a/products/product-001/releases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "releaseId": "release-2026-q3",
  "name": "Q3 Release",
  "scheduledFor": "2026-09-30"
}

### 3. Plan sprint
POST http://localhost:8080/agilepm/v1/tenants/tenant-a/products/product-001/sprints
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sprintId": "sprint-001",
  "name": "Sprint 1",
  "startsOn": "2026-07-01",
  "endsOn": "2026-07-15"
}

### 4. Request discussion
POST http://localhost:8080/agilepm/v1/tenants/tenant-a/products/product-001/discussion-requests

### 5. Attach discussion
PUT http://localhost:8080/agilepm/v1/tenants/tenant-a/products/product-001/discussion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "discussionId": "discussion-abc"
}

### 6. Query read model
GET http://localhost:8080/agilepm/v1/tenants/tenant-a/products/product-001
